summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the improvement of 58th Ave. S.W. from approximately 160 feet north of S.W. Andover St. to approximately 290 feet south of S.W. Orleans St.; and certain other streets, avenue and easements, by constructing sanitary sewers and otherwise improving the same, Local Improvement District No. 6681, and appropriating money from the Municipal Sewerage 1971 Construction Fund in aid thereof as a loan.
